HEADWORD: Marconi system
<hw>Mar*co"ni system</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Elec.)</fld> <def>A system
or wireless telegraphy developed by <person>G.
<etsep>Marconi</etsep></person>, an Italian physicist, in which Hertzian
waves are used in transmission and a coherer is used as the receiving
instrument.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

